cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and dependency parsing. It may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for parsing. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as dependency parsing is also used in image analysis, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as neural networks are used in the proposed approach.
